  <h1>About Me</h1>

  <p>
    I’m Angelo Meniconi — a freelance web designer, consultant, and multidisciplinary front-end developer.
    I help businesses, individuals, and brands around the world create professional, reliable websites
    and digital solutions that grow with them.
  </p>

  <p>
    With over 10 years of experience, I’ve delivered projects ranging from small brochure sites
    and personal portfolios to enterprise-level eCommerce platforms and B2B systems.
    My work combines strategy, design, and development to ensure each project is not just functional,
    but purposeful.
  </p>

  <p>
    My approach emphasizes <strong>clean, semantic code</strong>, strong performance, accessibility,
    and maintainability. I focus on building sites that are easy to use, easy to update,
    and designed to scale with your business.
  </p>

  <p>
    As a one-man consultancy, you work directly with me from start to finish — no account managers,
    no handovers, no unnecessary layers. This ensures clear communication, agility,
    and a personal, client-focused experience.
  </p>

  <p>
    I regularly work with small businesses, startups, creative professionals,
    and agencies needing trusted front-end development or consultancy support.
    Whether you’re launching a new project, improving an existing website,
    or looking for expert guidance, I provide clear, actionable solutions without the jargon.
  </p>

  <h2>How I Work</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Freelance:</strong> direct work with individuals and businesses, providing end-to-end development and consultancy.</li>
    <li><strong>White-Label:</strong> trusted development support for agencies looking for reliable front-end expertise.</li>
    <li><strong>Contract:</strong> short or long-term consultancy and front-end development to support digital projects.</li>
  </ul>

